    "Notes": "<br />\n <br />\n<strong>\n\n<i> <u> note:</u> \n</strong></i> <strong><i><u>Data displayed according to the user's authority with departments .<br><br><strong><i><u> Plan : </u></i></strong> Enter the plan to which you require to assign employees by clicking on the dropdown arrow to open the dropdown list and select the required option.<br><br><strong><i><u> Unassigned Employees : </u></i></strong> list the employees which don't assigned to plan.<br><br><strong><i><u> Assigned Employees :</u></i></strong> list the employees which assigned to plan.<br><br><strong><i><u> Down arrow :</u></i></strong> to assigned the selected employees from (unassigned list) to the selected plan. <br><br><strong><i><u>  Up arrow : </u></i></strong>to unassigned the selected employees from (assigned list)."
