  "EmployeeSchedule": {
    "Title": "Employees Schedules",
    "Plan": "Plan",
    "DateFrom": "Date From",
    "DateTo": "Date To",
    "ApplyNow": "Apply Now",
    "View": "View",
    "Notes": "<br />\n <br />\n<strong>\n\n<i> <u> note:</u> \n</strong></i> <strong><i><u>Data displayed according to the user's authority with departments .<br><br><strong><i><u> Plan: </u></i></strong>Select the plan to get employees assign to.<br><br><strong><i><u> Date From: </u></i></strong>Enter date apply schedule template from.  <br><br><strong><i><u> Date To: </u></i></strong> Enter date apply schedule template to.   <br><br><strong><i><u> Employee: </u></i></strong>  Select the employees you require to display them. <br><br><strong><i><u> Group: </u></i></strong> Select the groups you require to display the employees related to it . <br><br><strong><i><u> Department: </u></i></strong>  Select the departments you require to display the employees related to it . <br><br><strong><i><u> Job: </u></i></strong> Select the jobs you require to display the employees related to it. <br><br><strong><i><u> Location: </u></i></strong> Select the Locations you require to display the employees related to it. <br><br><strong><i><u> View: </u></i></strong> Click view button to view employee schedule for selected employees on calendar. <br><br><strong><i><u> Apply Template: </u></i></strong>  Select  apply template checkbox  to be able to apply template to employees. <br><br><strong><i><u> Template: </u></i></strong>  Select template from dropdown list. <br><br><strong><i><u> Apply Now: </u></i></strong>  Click apply now button to apply specified template to selected employees."
